currentDoc: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

currentSuggestions.original: You can not remember anything of your past lives, but everyone else in the theater starts rooting for you.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: You can not remember anything of your past lives, but everyone else in the theater starts rooting for you.

currentSuggestions.original: You are watching your next life because you have a contract with Death.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: You are watching your next life because you have a contract with Death.

currentSuggestions.original: They gather together and try to find a way out of this place.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: They gather together and try to find a way out of this place.

currentSuggestions.original: Eventually, you are all released to live your new life.
